item.description:
The band this Friday is Leaving Eden I have heard them before and truly enjoyed dancing to all there tunes, great variety of old and new songs.

We can meet for dinner for those of us who hate cooking on a Friday night, or just drop in later feo a few laughs, no cover charge and seperate checks. I will be there to introduce you and thenafter that will be on the dance floor. Looking forward to another fun filled night
item.how_to_find_us: We will be in the back end near the booths.
